data.description: MOVE-IN READY! Beautiful home on a corner lot, located in Ashland's desirable Meadowbrook Park Estate. New flooring, paint and all cabinets freshly refinished. Spacious floorplan with lots of natural lighting. Upstairs is a large Primary Suite with private exterior deck to enjoy sunset views! Primary Bath includes a double vanity, jetted tub and separate shower. Two additional bedrooms, laundry room and bath with a tub/shower complete. The main level kitchen has gas cooking, granite countertops, abundant storage with a walk-in pantry. Living room has a gas fireplace and built-ins. Sliding glass door opens onto a covered patio and easy care landscaping with mature trees. Landscaping maintained by the HOA. Finished two-car garage has separate mini-split for heat and air conditioning. 2021 updates include new exterior paint and air conditioning unit. Near Southern Oregon University, Downtown Ashland, Lithia Park, shopping, restaurants and entertainment.
